# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
# SaveYourself — .gitignore
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Personal / Private Assets ──────────────────
# If you have a personal logo, keep it out of the repo.
# See: README.md → "Customization" section.
assets/developer_logo.png

# ── Chrome Extension Build Artifacts ───────────
# Generated when packing the extension (chrome://extensions → Pack extension)
*.crx
*.pem
*.zip

# ── Windows / OS junk ──────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store

# ── Editor / IDE ────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.user

# ── Node (if ever added) ────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# ── Potential secrets / configs ─────────────────
# Never commit any file containing real passwords or API keys
*.env
*.env.*
config.local.*
secrets.*
